com.digitalglobe.platform2020.identity.configuration.collector

Interface UnopinionatedEndpointCollector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnnotationBasedOpinionatedEndpointCollector, CamelRestUnopinionatedEndpointCollector, CXFEndpointCollector, SpringMVCEndpointCollector

    public interface UnopinionatedEndpointCollector
    Collect endpoints (combination of HTTP method and URI) that do not have an associated security opinion
    Author:
    Josh Ghiloni

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> collectUnopinionatedEndpoints()
      Collect all endpoints that have no opinions.

    • Method Detail

      • collectUnopinionatedEndpoints

        java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> collectUnopinionatedEndpoints()
                                                              throws EndpointsNotInitializedException
        Collect all endpoints that have no opinions. These endpoints may have wildcards. Ideally, this should return a value such that org.springframework.util.CollectionUtils#isEmpty(java.util.Collection) returns true. If not, your microservice will fail to start.
        Returns:
        a collection of objects representing a list of unopinionated endpoints.
        Throws:
        EndpointsNotInitializedException - if the collector is not ready to collect endpoints yet
